# Aegis OS package overlay — appended to releng's packages.x86_64 by build.sh,
# which also appends `aegis` itself (built from ./package into a local repo).
# These are the gaming/graphics/audio userland; the `aegis` package pulls the
# kiosk runtime (cage, electron, seatd, pipewire, ...) as hard dependencies.

# --- graphics: open-source Vulkan for all vendors + software fallback ---
mesa
vulkan-icd-loader
vulkan-swrast
vulkan-radeon
vulkan-intel
lib32-mesa
lib32-vulkan-icd-loader
lib32-vulkan-radeon
lib32-vulkan-intel

# --- gaming: Steam + Proton (Proton games run under Xwayland) ---
steam
xorg-xwayland

# --- audio (also aegis deps; listed so the live env has them too) ---
pipewire
pipewire-pulse
pipewire-alsa
wireplumber
libpulse

# --- Wayland kiosk: cage compositor + Electron (the audio-reactive sphere) ---
cage
seatd
electron
dbus
